{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850748800,"sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","part":{"id":"prt_d78f324be001Eu1RkdbDqx3A9e","messageID":"msg_d78f25e510012omQqTeZpMLdiM","sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:12","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/plan.md","content":"# AR-007 Implementation Plan\n\n## Phase 1: Controller Foundation\n\n- [ ] Set up controller-runtime manager\n- [ ] Configure scheme with AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter types\n- [ ] Implement basic controller structure\n- [ ] Add health checks and metrics setup\n\n## Phase 2: Resource Watchers\n\n- [ ] Implement AgentRuntime resource watcher\n- [ ] Implement CodeInterpreter resource watcher\n- [ ] Configure event filters (generation, deletion timestamp)\n- [ ] Add watch predicates for relevant changes only\n\n## Phase 3: Reconcile Loop\n\n- [ ] Implement AgentRuntime reconciler\n- [ ] Implement CodeInterpreter reconciler\n- [ ] Add request queue with workqueue\n- [ ] Implement rate limiting configuration\n\n## Phase 4: Finalizer Management\n\n- [ ] Add finalizer for AgentRuntime resources\n- [ ] Add finalizer for CodeInterpreter resources\n- [ ] Implement finalizer handler for graceful deletion\n- [ ] Handle cleanup before finalizer removal\n\n## Phase 5: Status Management\n\n- [ ] Define status conditions for reconciliation\n- [ ] Implement status update logic\n- [ ] Add condition transitions (Ready, Pending, Failed)\n- [ ] Update observedGeneration tracking\n\n## Phase 6: Error Handling & Backoff\n\n- [ ] Implement exponential backoff for retries\n- [ ] Configure max retries and backoff parameters\n- [ ] Distinguish transient vs permanent errors\n- [ ] Add reconciliation error metrics\n\n## Phase 7: OwnerReference Management\n\n- [ ] Set OwnerReference on created child resources\n- [ ] Handle cascade deletion via garbage collector\n- [ ] Verify owner chain integrity\n\n## Phase 8: Metrics & Observability\n\n- [ ] Expose reconciliation duration metrics\n- [ ] Add reconciliation error counters\n- [ ] Implement controller-runtime metrics\n- [ ] Add structured logging for reconciliation events\n\n## Phase 9: Integration\n\n- [ ] Integrate with WorkloadManager service layer\n- [ ] Connect to AR-005/AR-006 handlers\n- [ ] Verify end-to-end reconciliation flow\n- [ ] Add integration tests\n\n## Phase 10: Testing & Validation\n\n- [ ] Unit tests for reconciler logic\n- [ ] Integration tests with fake client\n- [ ] E2E tests with kind cluster\n- [ ] Verify metrics collection\n- [ ] Performance testing for concurrent reconciliations\n\n## Checklist\n\n- [ ] Code follows Go best practices\n- [ ] All exported functions have documentation\n- [ ] Error handling is consistent with controller-runtime patterns\n- [ ] Configuration is externalized (resync period, backoff)\n- [ ] Tests cover happy path and error cases\n- [ ] Integration with existing WorkloadManager verified\n- [ ] Metrics and logging are documented\n- [ ] Finalizer behavior is tested\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-006/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/plan.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/plan.md","time":{"start":1775850748781,"end":1775850748799}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850748802,"sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","part":{"id":"prt_d78f36c44001pjfT5mrkffJcWh","messageID":"msg_d78f25e510012omQqTeZpMLdiM","sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:13","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/tests.md","content":"# AR-007 Test Strategy\n\n## Unit Tests\n\n### Reconciler Tests\n\n- Test successful reconciliation of AgentRuntime\n- Test successful reconciliation of CodeInterpreter\n- Test finalizer addition on new resources\n- Test finalizer cleanup on deletion\n- Test status condition updates\n\n### Error Handling Tests\n\n- Test exponential backoff behavior\n- Test max retry limit enforcement\n- Test transient vs permanent error classification\n- Test requeue on conflict errors\n\n## Integration Tests\n\n### Controller-Runtime Integration\n\n- Test watch events are received correctly\n- Test workqueue behavior\n- Test rate limiting configuration\n- Test scheme registration\n\n### Resource Lifecycle Tests\n\n- Test create → reconcile → ready flow\n- Test update → reconcile flow\n- Test delete → finalizer → cleanup flow\n- Test OwnerReference propagation\n\n## E2E Tests\n\n### Kind Cluster Tests\n\n- Deploy controller to kind cluster\n- Create AgentRuntime CR and verify reconciliation\n- Create CodeInterpreter CR and verify reconciliation\n- Test deletion with finalizers\n- Verify metrics endpoint\n\n## Test Coverage Goals\n\n- Reconciler logic: >= 80%\n- Error handling: >= 80%\n- Finalizer management: >= 80%\n- Status updates: >= 80%\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-006/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2