{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850748803,"sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","part":{"id":"prt_d78f38ff4001A4ezUxCTQKbHea","messageID":"msg_d78f25e510012omQqTeZpMLdiM","sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/tasks.md","content":"# AR-007 Task Breakdown\n\n## T001: Controller Manager Setup\n**Status:** Open  \n**Assignee:** TBD  \n**Estimated Hours:** 4\n\n- Initialize controller-runtime manager\n- Configure scheme with CRD types\n- Set up health probes and metrics\n- Add graceful shutdown handling\n\n## T002: Resource Watchers\n**Status:** Open  \n**Assignee:** TBD  \n**Estimated Hours:** 6\n\n- Implement AgentRuntime watcher\n- Implement CodeInterpreter watcher\n- Configure event predicates\n- Filter irrelevant events\n\n## T003: AgentRuntime Reconciler\n**Status:** Open  \n**Assignee:** TBD  \n**Estimated Hours:** 8\n\n- Implement reconcile loop\n- Add finalizer management\n- Handle create/update/delete events\n- Update status conditions\n\n## T004: CodeInterpreter Reconciler\n**Status:** Open  \n**Assignee:** TBD  \n**Estimated Hours:** 8\n\n- Implement reconcile loop\n- Add finalizer management\n- Handle create/update/delete events\n- Update status conditions\n\n## T005: Error Handling & Backoff\n**Status:** Open  \n**Assignee:** TBD  \n**Estimated Hours:** 4\n\n- Implement exponential backoff\n- Configure retry policies\n- Classify error types\n- Add error metrics\n\n## T006: Metrics & Observability\n**Status:** Open  \n**Assignee:** TBD  \n**Estimated Hours:** 4\n\n- Add reconciliation metrics\n- Configure structured logging\n- Implement tracing hooks\n- Document observability\n\n## T007: Service Layer Integration\n**Status:** Open  \n**Assignee:** TBD  \n**Estimated Hours:** 6\n\n- Integrate with WorkloadManager\n- Con