{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850748804,"sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","part":{"id":"prt_d78f3d369001Bw2T8DM2W47ghJ","messageID":"msg_d78f25e510012omQqTeZpMLdiM","sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:15","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/notes.md","content":"# AR-007 Notes\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### Controller-Runtime Version\n\nUse controller-runtime v0.20.x which aligns with Kubernetes 1.32+.\n\n### Key Dependencies\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/manager\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/reconcile\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/controller\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/handler\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/source\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\"\n)\n```\n\n### Reconcile Result Patterns\n\n- Return `reconcile.Result{Requeue: true}` for transient errors\n- Return `reconcile.Result{RequeueAfter: duration}` for backoff\n- Return `reconcile.Result{}` for successful completion\n- Return error for retry with exponential backoff\n\n### Finalizer Naming Convention\n\nUse `\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/finalizer\"` as the finalizer name.\n\n## References\n\n- [controller-runtime Documentation](https://pkg.go.dev/sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime)\n- [Kubebuilder Book - CronJob Tutorial](https://book.kubebuilder.io/cronjob-tutorial/cronjob-tutorial)\n- [Kubernetes Controller Guidelines](https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/sig-api-machinery/controllers.md)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-006/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/notes.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/notes.md","time":{"start":1775850748789,"end":1775850748804}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850748807,"sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","part":{"id":"prt_d78f2b1a9001fYdvOck9icHD6y","messageID":"msg_d78f25e510012omQqTeZpMLdiM","sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_boding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/design.md","content":"# AR-007 Design: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n\n## Overview\n\n**AR ID:** AR-007  \n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** Large  \n\nThe K8s Reconciler Controller provides event-driven reconciliation for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs in the AgentCube system. It uses controller-runtime to watch resources, manage lifecycle transitions, and ensure cluster state matches desired state.\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Design\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Kubernetes API Server                                   │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │                     CRD Resources                                     │  │\n│  │  ┌────────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐                     │  │\n│  │  │ AgentRuntime       │  │ CodeInterpreter    │                     │  │\n│  │  │ (watch)            │  │ (watch)            │                     │  │\n│  │  └────────┬───────────┘  └────────┬───────────┘                     │  │\n│  └───────────┼───────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│              │                       │                                       │\n└──────────────┼───────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────┘\n               │                       │\n               ▼                       ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Reconciler Controller                                   │\n│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │                    Controller Manager                                   │ │\n│  │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n│  │  │                      Source (Watches)                             │ │ │\n│  │  │  ┌─────────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────┐              │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ AgentRuntime Source │  │ CodeInterpreter Src │              │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ · Create Events     │  │ · Create Events     │              │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ · Update Events     │  │ · Update Events     │              │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ · Delete Events     │  │ · Delete Events     │              │ │ │\n│  │  │  └──────────┬──────────┘  └──────────┬──────────┘              │ │ │\n│  │  └─────────────┼────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────┘ │ │\n│  │                │                        │                           │ │\n│  │  ┌─────────────▼────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────┐ │ │\n│  │  │                      Work Queue                                   │ │ │\n│  │  │  · Rate limiting                                                   │ │ │\n│  │  │  · Retry with exponential backoff                                 │ │ │\n│  │  └────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n│  │                               │                                       │ │\n│  │  ┌────────────────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n│  │  │                   Reconcile Loop                                  │ │ │\n│  │  │  ┌────────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐                │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ AgentRuntime       │  │ CodeInterpreter    │                │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ Reconciler         │  │ Reconciler         │                │ │ │\n│  │  │  └────────────────────┘  └────────────────────┘                │ │ │\n│  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Components\n\n### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n\n---\n\n## Interfaces\n\n### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n\n---\n\n## Data Flow\n\n### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- [controller-runtime](https://pkg.go.dev/sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime)\n- [AR-003: client-go Generated Code](../AR-003/)\n- [AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework](../AR-004/)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-006/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_boding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_boding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/design.md","time":{"start":1775850748778,"end":1775850748806}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850749178,"sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","part":{"id":"prt_d78f26b39001q80i9z7UBBgks9","messageID":"msg_d78f25e510012omQqTeZpMLdiM","sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:10","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-007\ntitle: K8s Reconciler 控制器\nmodule: pkg/workloadmanager\nlanguage: Go\nsize: L\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n# Module: pkg/workloadmanager\n# Language: Go\n# Size: L\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: reconciler-controller\n  description: |\n    Implement the Kubernetes Reconciler controller for the WorkloadManager.\n    This controller watches AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRs, reconciles\n    their desired state with actual cluster state, and manages the lifecycle\n    of sandbox resources. It integrates with the controller-runtime framework\n    and provides event-driven reconciliation with proper error handling and\n    exponential backoff.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - CRD resource watchers for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n    - Reconciliation loop implementation with controller-runtime\n    - Event-driven reconciliation on resource changes\n    - Exponential backoff for failed reconciliations\n    - Finalizer handling for graceful deletion\n    - Status updates and condition management\n    - OwnerReference management for garbage collection\n    - Integration with existing WorkloadManager service layer\n    - Reconcile queue with rate limiting\n    - Metrics and observability hooks\n  out:\n    - CRD type definitions (handled in AR-001/AR-002)\n    - client-go generated code (handled in AR-003)\n    - HTTP service framework (handled in AR-004)\n    - Sandbox creation/deletion logic (handled in AR-005/AR-006)\n    - Multi-cluster reconciliation (separate AR)\n    - Leader election for HA (separate AR)\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - Controller watches AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRs\n  - Reconciliation loop processes create/update/delete events\n  - Exponential backoff for transient failures (configurable)\n  - Finalizers ensure graceful resource cleanup\n  - Status conditions accurately reflect resource state\n  - OwnerReferences are properly set for garbage collection\n  - Integration with WorkloadManager service layer\n  - Metrics exposed for reconciliation latency and errors\n  - Unit tests achieve >= 80% coverage\n  - Integration tests verify end-to-end reconciliation\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime Types\n  - AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter Types\n  - AR-003: client-go Generated Code\n  - AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework\n  - AR-005: Sandbox Creation Handler\n  - AR-006: Sandbox Deletion and Lifecycle Management\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: L\n  story_points: 8\n  days: 5\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-006/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/spec.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775850748772,"end":1775850749176}}}}
