   WorkloadManager HTTP Server (AR-004)                      │\n29: │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n30: │  │                         Router Layer                                    │ │\n\n(Showing lines 1-30 of 438. Use offset=31 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-006 Design: Sandbox Deletion and Lifecycle Management\n\n## Overview\n\n**AR ID:** AR-006  \n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** Medium  \n\nThe Sandbox Deletion and Lifecycle Management component provides comprehensive lifecycle control for sandboxes in the AgentCube system. It handles graceful shutdown, resource cleanup, idle detection, and orphan management while integrating with the WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework (AR-004) and Sandbox Creation Handler (AR-005).\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Design\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                       External Clients                                       │","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-006/design.md","time":{"start":1775850775387,"end":1775850775399}}}}
