{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850800268,"sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","part":{"id":"prt_d78f46ad2001EZsERNXPK9ttTT","messageID":"msg_d78f46395001M4XS4Rcboay0Iu","sessionID":"ses_2870e36d0ffe4mIUYGl99RSV6W","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:20","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-007 Design: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n\n## Overview\n\n**AR ID:** AR-007  \n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** Large  \n\nThe K8s Reconciler Controller provides event-driven reconciliation for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs in the AgentCube system. It uses controller-runtime to watch resources, manage lifecycle transitions, and ensure cluster state matches desired state.\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Design\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Kubernetes API Server                                   │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │                     CRD Resources                                     │  │\n│  │  ┌────────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐                     │  │\n│  │  │ AgentRuntime       │  │ CodeInterpreter    │                     │  │\n│  │  │ (watch)            │  │ (watch)            │                     │  │\n│  │  └────────┬───────────┘  └────────┬───────────┘                     │  │\n│  └───────────┼───────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│              │                       │                                       │\n└──────────────┼───────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────┘\n               │                       │\n               ▼                       ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Reconciler Controller                                   │\n│  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │                    Controller Manager                                   │ │\n│  │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n│  │  │                      Source (Watches)                             │ │ │\n│  │  │  ┌─────────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────┐              │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ AgentRuntime Source │  │ CodeInterpreter Src │              │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ · Create Events     │  │ · Create Events     │              │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ · Update Events     │  │ · Update Events     │              │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ · Delete Events     │  │ · Delete Events     │              │ │ │\n│  │  │  └──────────┬──────────┘  └──────────┬──────────┘              │ │ │\n│  │  └─────────────┼────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────┘ │ │\n│  │                │                        │                           │ │\n│  │  ┌─────────────▼────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────┐ │ │\n│  │  │                      Work Queue                                   │ │ │\n│  │  │  · Rate limiting                                                   │ │ │\n│  │  │  · Retry with exponential backoff                                 │ │ │\n│  │  └────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n│  │                               │                                       │ │\n│  │  ┌────────────────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n│  │  │                   Reconcile Loop                                  │ │ │\n│  │  │  ┌────────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐                │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ AgentRuntime       │  │ CodeInterpreter    │                │ │ │\n│  │  │  │ Reconciler         │  │ Reconciler         │                │ │ │\n│  │  │  └────────────────────┘  └────────────────────┘                │ │ │\n│  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Components\n\n### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n\n---\n\n## Interfaces\n\n### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n\n---\n\n## Data Flow\n\n### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- [controller-runtime](https://pkg.go.dev/sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime)\n- [AR-003: client-go Generated Code](../AR-003/)\n- [AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework](../AR-004/)\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-006/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/design.md","time":{"start":1775850800254,"end":1775850800264}}}}
